name: Serie Gran Reserva 1988
additionalNotes: Warped Serie Gran Reserva 1988 is another yet collaboration between Kyle Gellis and Casa Fernandez. Gran Reserva 1988 is a single-size Nicaraguan puro line. The wrapper leaf is a Corojo '99 while the filler is a blend of Corojo '99. All Nicaraguan Tobacco produced by AGANORSA.
